00:03:13.800 --> 00:03:17.350
Hey. If you fall asleep here,
you might catch a cold again.

00:03:21.970 --> 00:03:27.020
Mahiru was busy all day today
making food for the new year.

00:03:30.970 --> 00:03:35.560
She said she'd recovered from the cold,
but it looks like she still overdid it.

00:03:36.950 --> 00:03:40.240
So I get why. I get it, but...

00:03:42.070 --> 00:03:45.670
Mahiru, wake up. Mahiru!

00:03:52.910 --> 00:03:56.020
Man, she smells so good!

00:03:57.500 --> 00:03:59.080
What should I do?!

00:04:01.010 --> 00:04:03.970
The only countermeasures
I can think of are...

00:04:04.280 --> 00:04:04.800
Boo!

00:04:04.800 --> 00:04:05.850
Wha—?!

00:04:05.850 --> 00:04:07.050
Startle her awake.

00:04:09.470 --> 00:04:14.520
I don't think she'd take kindly to such a rude
awakening when she's so tired already.

00:04:15.310 --> 00:04:16.690
Shiina

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:16.690
Two:

00:04:17.240 --> 00:04:18.690
Take Mahiru back home.

00:04:21.060 --> 00:04:23.760
I can't fumble through
a girl's clothes for a key

00:04:23.760 --> 00:04:26.110
and go into her room without permission!

00:04:26.110 --> 00:04:28.200
Not a chance.

00:04:32.580 --> 00:04:33.460
Three:

00:04:33.930 --> 00:04:37.290
Put her in my bed while I sleep on the couch.

00:04:38.080 --> 00:04:41.820
I think that's the best I can do.
A good compromise.

00:04:50.440 --> 00:04:51.670
Good night.

00:05:02.250 --> 00:05:05.400
She's in for a real shock when she wakes up.

00:05:09.350 --> 00:05:10.120
Huh?!

00:05:13.400 --> 00:05:15.400
She isn't even up yet!

00:05:28.260 --> 00:05:30.760
She shouldn't drop her guard like this.

00:05:31.310 --> 00:05:34.150
Sure looks cute when sleeping, though.

00:05:51.330 --> 00:05:52.230
Phew.

00:06:06.540 --> 00:06:07.420
Huh?

00:06:08.020 --> 00:06:09.050
M-Morning.

00:06:09.390 --> 00:06:11.680
Um, good... morning!

00:06:12.250 --> 00:06:15.600
You fell asleep at my place,
so I let you sleep here.

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:16.310
Nothing happened.

00:06:17.030 --> 00:06:20.180
In fact, you should thank me
for doing absolutely nothing.

00:06:24.670 --> 00:06:26.940
What is happening here?

00:06:27.520 --> 00:06:31.050
Amane-kun, do you really like
touching cheeks?

00:06:31.050 --> 00:06:31.720
Huh?

00:06:31.720 --> 00:06:36.410
You touched mine on Christmas
and then before I fell asleep last night.

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:38.800
You were awake the whole time?

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:41.210
Huh? N-No, it's just...

00:06:41.210 --> 00:06:44.440
I woke up for a second
when you put me in bed.

00:06:44.440 --> 00:06:48.220
What else could I do
but pretend to be asleep?

00:06:48.590 --> 00:06:51.300
And you didn't stop to think
I might try something?

00:06:51.300 --> 00:06:55.310
I didn't think you would, at least...

00:06:55.900 --> 00:07:00.310
I might have been pretending
just to make sure you wouldn't.

00:07:00.800 --> 00:07:03.810
Well, I guess it's okay if it helps you trust me,

00:07:04.280 --> 00:07:07.920
but you can't do that again.
I'm still a guy, you know.

00:07:07.920 --> 00:07:10.950
Uh... yes, I know that.

00:07:10.950 --> 00:07:13.240
Or did you want me to make a move?

00:07:14.620 --> 00:07:17.220
How could you even say that?!

00:07:18.600 --> 00:07:21.530
Well, you are in my bed.

00:07:27.810 --> 00:07:29.880
It's been half a year, Amane.

00:07:30.220 --> 00:07:32.110
Good to see you, Dad.

00:07:32.110 --> 00:07:35.800
You weren't that polite to your mom!

00:07:35.800 --> 00:07:38.740
Yeah, because you surprised me and barged in.

00:07:40.900 --> 00:07:42.440
What's the luggage for?

00:07:42.440 --> 00:07:44.970
We brought some things with us.

00:07:44.970 --> 00:07:47.290
But first, where's Mahiru-chan?

00:07:47.290 --> 00:07:47.940
Inside.

00:07:48.760 --> 00:07:51.110
Mahiru-chan, it's been so long!

00:07:51.480 --> 00:07:53.100
It's good to see you again.

00:07:53.100 --> 00:07:56.810
So long? It hasn't even been a month.

00:07:56.810 --> 00:07:58.790
Well, it felt like a long time to me.

00:08:00.480 --> 00:08:04.000
Amane-kun's brother... no, father?

00:08:04.400 --> 00:08:08.630
Nice to meet you.
I'm Amane's father, Shuto Fujimiya.

00:08:09.230 --> 00:08:12.830
Shihoko-san told me
all about you, Shiina-san.

00:08:12.830 --> 00:08:15.740
Thank you for looking after my son.

00:08:15.740 --> 00:08:19.150
Pleased to meet you. I'm Mahiru Shiina.

00:08:19.150 --> 00:08:22.480
Amane-kun has actually
been a great help to me.

00:08:22.480 --> 00:08:26.090
Oh, dear. You don't need to be so modest.

00:08:26.090 --> 00:08:28.480
We know how much of a slob Amane is.

00:08:28.480 --> 00:08:31.130
Yeah, sorry for being a slob.

00:08:31.130 --> 00:08:34.600
Come on now, Shihoko-san.
Don't say things like that.

00:08:34.600 --> 00:08:35.570
All right.

00:08:35.570 --> 00:08:36.460
Amane.

00:08:36.460 --> 00:08:37.390
Hmm?

00:08:37.390 --> 00:08:41.880
She always takes care of you,
so I hope you show her some appreciation.

00:08:41.880 --> 00:08:43.410
Y-Yeah.

00:08:43.410 --> 00:08:47.420
Yes, Amane-kun
is surprisingly very considerate.

00:08:47.420 --> 00:08:50.280
"Surprisingly"?
What do you mean "surprisingly"?

00:08:50.280 --> 00:08:51.680
You know...

00:08:51.680 --> 00:08:54.880
I'm glad to see you both get along so well.

00:08:54.880 --> 00:08:59.320
Amane, you'd better not cause
too much trouble for Shiina-san, okay?

00:08:59.920 --> 00:09:01.010
I know.

00:09:01.370 --> 00:09:06.020
And Shiina-san, if Amane ever acts badly,
feel free to give him an earful.

00:09:06.480 --> 00:09:08.590
This kid is more cooperative than he looks,

00:09:08.590 --> 00:09:11.440
so I'm sure he'd improve any
bad behavior you point out.

00:09:11.440 --> 00:09:15.320
Amane-kun is very kind to me.
He doesn't behave badly.

00:09:15.320 --> 00:09:18.200
But he might have some flaws...

00:09:18.620 --> 00:09:21.660
Like how he's always
so cool without even trying.

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:23.990
Oh.

00:09:25.140 --> 00:09:26.710
Heh?

00:09:28.050 --> 00:09:29.670
What was that for?

00:09:31.110 --> 00:09:32.150
Here you go.

00:09:33.310 --> 00:09:36.970
Thank you so much, Mahiru-chan.
You seem like you're used to things here.

00:09:36.970 --> 00:09:38.460
Y-Yes, I am.

00:09:39.050 --> 00:09:40.400
By the way, Amane.

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:41.070
Hmm?

00:09:41.070 --> 00:09:44.430
You started calling
Mahiru-chan by her first name, right?

00:09:45.260 --> 00:09:51.210
This is so nice. I'm tickled to see
my son get along with such a pretty girl.

00:09:51.210 --> 00:09:54.830
Meanwhile I'm in a cold sweat,
worried you'll slip back into old habits

00:09:54.830 --> 00:09:56.990
and start brutally teasing him.

00:09:56.990 --> 00:10:00.030
Oh, my. But wouldn't you stop me, Shuto-san?

00:10:00.360 --> 00:10:03.960
If you're aware that it's wrong,
you should probably try to fix it.

00:10:03.960 --> 00:10:06.810
But I guess that quirk is one
reason I fell for you, Shihoko-san.

00:10:06.810 --> 00:10:07.660
What can I say?

00:10:08.020 --> 00:10:10.290
Oh, Shuto-san, you!

00:10:11.890 --> 00:10:14.590
Your parents get along quite well.

00:10:14.590 --> 00:10:17.670
Yeah, they do.
They're always like this at home.

00:10:19.030 --> 00:10:20.640
Is that right?

00:10:21.080 --> 00:10:24.810
Hey, kids. You haven't gone
on your first shrine visit yet, have you?

00:10:24.810 --> 00:10:25.790
No.

00:10:25.790 --> 00:10:28.880
I thought so! That's why I brought a kimono!

00:10:31.230 --> 00:10:35.280
It's always been my dream to take
my daughter on a shrine visit in a kimono,

00:10:35.680 --> 00:10:38.340
and I thought Mahiru-chan
would look just gorgeous.

00:10:39.450 --> 00:10:43.480
Well, if Mahiru's okay with it,
why not dress her up and take her?

00:10:43.480 --> 00:10:46.500
Oh? And why don't you think you're coming?

00:10:46.500 --> 00:10:51.080
Yeah, if the kids at school caught
me out with Mahiru, it'd be a mess.

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:53.960
So just don't get caught.

00:10:57.620 --> 00:11:00.300
Well, I guess it isn't awful.

00:11:00.730 --> 00:11:03.220
When you get dressed up
without putting up a fuss,

00:11:03.220 --> 00:11:05.470
I think you look very handsome, Amane.

00:11:05.470 --> 00:11:08.200
That's a little too generous
even for a parent.

00:11:08.200 --> 00:11:10.520
Itsuki was saying the same thing, though.

00:11:10.520 --> 00:11:13.150
Oh, that Itsuki-kun?

00:11:13.150 --> 00:11:17.390
He must be a really good kid
if you vouch for him.

00:11:18.680 --> 00:11:22.160
Yeah, he's a good guy.
Probably too good for me.

00:11:22.850 --> 00:11:24.910
Are you glad you came here, Amane?

00:11:30.440 --> 00:11:33.360
Yeah, I am. It's a lot easier.

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:35.160
Good. I'm glad to hear it.

00:11:35.160 --> 00:11:36.500
Thanks for waiting!

00:11:40.760 --> 00:11:42.270
Well?

00:11:42.270 --> 00:11:46.140
Mahiru-chan is a great model,
so it was a very rewarding process!

00:11:47.520 --> 00:11:49.890
Yes, you look very good in it.

00:11:49.890 --> 00:11:53.400
Come on, Amane. Tell her what you think.

00:11:54.020 --> 00:11:55.650
I th-think it looks good on you.

00:11:57.150 --> 00:11:59.530
You're really no good at this, are you?

00:12:02.030 --> 00:12:05.180
All right. Shuto-san,
should we get the car ready?

00:12:05.180 --> 00:12:06.280
Yeah, let's do that.

00:12:07.800 --> 00:12:09.290
Thank you for waiting.

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:13.300
Is something wrong?

00:12:13.960 --> 00:12:15.960
I just think it looks good on you.

00:12:16.930 --> 00:12:19.800
You really nail the
"pure Japanese beauty" look.

00:12:20.280 --> 00:12:22.360
Cute and beautiful at the same time.

00:12:24.960 --> 00:12:28.090
Ah, I forgot how much you hate compliments.

00:12:28.090 --> 00:12:28.990
Sorry.

00:12:28.990 --> 00:12:31.930
N-No, that... isn't it.

00:12:32.350 --> 00:12:34.480
Amane-kun, you kind of look...

00:12:34.480 --> 00:12:35.460
Kind of look...?

00:12:40.430 --> 00:12:41.510
Amane-kun.

00:12:41.510 --> 00:12:42.110
Hmm?

00:12:42.110 --> 00:12:46.240
Um, I think you look really good, too.

00:12:52.080 --> 00:12:54.070
Now that's just unfair.

