I do around the other two.

00:15:57.640 --> 00:15:59.470
Gimme a sip!

00:15:59.820 --> 00:16:00.650
Chitose!

00:16:00.650 --> 00:16:02.820
We're friends! It's fine, it's fine!

00:16:06.500 --> 00:16:10.240
Do you always do that sort of
thing with Akazawa-san?

00:16:10.240 --> 00:16:12.910
Yeah, we're all friends.

00:16:12.910 --> 00:16:14.340
In that case...

00:16:18.020 --> 00:16:21.710
You and I are close friends,
so I'm okay with it.

00:16:21.710 --> 00:16:23.590
O-Okay.

00:16:27.210 --> 00:16:29.760
I feel bad. You must be exhausted.

00:16:29.760 --> 00:16:33.370
No, I'm fine. I had a good time.

00:16:33.370 --> 00:16:34.220
Good.

00:16:34.220 --> 00:16:35.500
Also...

00:16:35.500 --> 00:16:36.470
Also?

00:16:37.410 --> 00:16:41.610
I feel like I got a taste of real happiness.

00:16:49.020 --> 00:16:51.100
E-Excuse me?

00:16:51.100 --> 00:16:52.250
It's nothing.

00:16:52.250 --> 00:16:56.070
This isn't nothing. You'll mess up my hair.

00:16:56.490 --> 00:16:57.700
So I can't?

00:16:58.120 --> 00:17:00.360
I'm not saying you can't,

00:17:00.360 --> 00:17:02.700
but at least warn me first.

00:17:02.700 --> 00:17:03.960
I'm touching.

00:17:03.960 --> 00:17:06.170
Not after the fact!

00:17:06.170 --> 00:17:07.240
Sorry.

00:17:08.740 --> 00:17:12.170
Oh, boy. This is all right with me,

00:17:12.820 --> 00:17:17.780
but you shouldn't pat most girls
on the head so casually.

00:17:18.400 --> 00:17:20.560
Well, I wouldn't do it to anyone else.

00:17:22.290 --> 00:17:23.980
Huh? Oh.

00:17:23.980 --> 00:17:26.980
What? You wanted me to keep going?

00:17:27.880 --> 00:17:29.860
Please stop teasing me!

00:17:35.480 --> 00:17:37.420
Maybe I overdid it.

00:17:37.420 --> 00:17:38.730
A-Amane-kun.

00:17:40.290 --> 00:17:41.240
What is it?

00:17:41.240 --> 00:17:43.700
Amane-kun, you dummy!

00:17:47.430 --> 00:17:49.380
Who's the real dummy, though?

00:17:52.720 --> 00:17:54.800
Are you going back already?

00:17:55.240 --> 00:17:57.420
Yes, we don't have a choice.

00:17:57.420 --> 00:18:02.040
I would have loved to stay another
day or two, but we have work.

00:18:02.040 --> 00:18:04.510
Well, we'll have another chance.

00:18:04.510 --> 00:18:07.770
However, I think next time is Amane's turn.

00:18:08.170 --> 00:18:11.150
I know, I know. I'll go visit in the summer.

00:18:11.530 --> 00:18:12.320
Geez.

00:18:12.800 --> 00:18:15.570
They're pressuring me
to bring Mahiru along, too.

00:18:16.050 --> 00:18:19.820
As you can see,
our Amane can be a little stubborn,

00:18:19.820 --> 00:18:23.200
but if you take a close look,
he's a straightforward and gentle kid.

00:18:23.960 --> 00:18:26.490
I'd be thrilled if you'd continue
your friendship with him.

00:18:26.490 --> 00:18:29.710
Do you have to say that now?
I'm standing right here.

00:18:30.220 --> 00:18:34.840
I'm constantly reminded of what a kind
and sincere person Amane-kun is.

00:18:35.230 --> 00:18:39.200
As for staying friends, that's
something I'd even ask for myself.

00:18:39.200 --> 00:18:43.100
I'm glad to hear that. How reassuring.

00:18:43.100 --> 00:18:45.690
Yes, really! Isn't that nice, Amane?

00:18:45.690 --> 00:18:46.600
We'll visit again, okay?

00:18:46.600 --> 00:18:50.100
Fujimiya

00:18:47.720 --> 00:18:50.100
You don't need to
flatter me in front of them.

00:18:50.410 --> 00:18:54.020
Do you think I'd flatter you
with compliments I didn't mean?

00:18:54.480 --> 00:18:58.440
N-Not directly to me, but you
might for my parents' sake.

00:18:59.320 --> 00:19:00.780
Please listen to me.

00:19:01.310 --> 00:19:06.110
I truly think you have a wonderful
personality, Amane-kun.

00:19:06.110 --> 00:19:08.960
That's why I trust you enough
to spend time with you like this.

00:19:09.440 --> 00:19:11.540
I didn't mean it as mere flattery.

00:19:11.540 --> 00:19:13.210
O-Oh.

00:19:13.840 --> 00:19:15.750
But it's all right as long as you understand.

00:19:16.280 --> 00:19:19.130
So, shall we start getting ready for lunch?

00:19:19.440 --> 00:19:21.720
Trust, huh?

00:19:23.140 --> 00:19:25.880
I'm so glad I moved here.

00:19:27.760 --> 00:19:29.230
Hey, hey, did you hear?

00:19:29.230 --> 00:19:32.760
There's a rumor that Shiina-san
in class A has a boyfriend.

00:19:32.760 --> 00:19:34.210
I did, I did!

00:19:34.210 --> 00:19:37.650
They say she was holding hands
with some boy on a shrine visit.

00:19:37.650 --> 00:19:40.880
Shiina-san didn't seem like
she'd give anyone a shot,

00:19:40.880 --> 00:19:42.720
but maybe that was because
she had a boyfriend.

00:19:42.720 --> 00:19:47.980
They said he looked really cool and
they'd never seen him at school before.

00:19:47.980 --> 00:19:51.020
You think he's from another school, then?

00:19:51.990 --> 00:19:53.130
Hey, Amane.

00:19:53.130 --> 00:19:53.790
Don't care.

00:19:54.440 --> 00:19:56.040
I haven't said anything yet.

00:19:56.040 --> 00:19:57.500
Not my problem.

00:19:58.260 --> 00:19:59.440
Very well, sir.

00:19:59.440 --> 00:20:00.090
H-Hey!

00:20:00.810 --> 00:20:03.580
You try to hide it but you
do have a nice face.

00:20:03.580 --> 00:20:07.100
Coming from you,
it only sounds like you're teasing.

00:20:07.990 --> 00:20:10.230
You're always like this, man.

00:20:11.060 --> 00:20:11.980
Shut up.

00:20:12.960 --> 00:20:15.980
So our Shiina-san finally
has a boyfriend, huh?

00:20:17.840 --> 00:20:20.260
They're talking about it all over school.

00:20:23.320 --> 00:20:28.090
It's good that nobody realized it was you,
but it's quite a misunderstanding.

00:20:28.590 --> 00:20:31.190
It's going to be difficult to clear up.

00:20:31.790 --> 00:20:35.180
Is holding hands enough
to make me your boyfriend?

00:20:35.180 --> 00:20:39.750
I wouldn't know. For now, I insisted
that it was just an acquaintance.

00:20:40.880 --> 00:20:44.030
We just have to wait for the talk to die down.

00:20:44.030 --> 00:20:46.810
Yeah, I guess that's all we can do.

00:20:46.810 --> 00:20:48.010
Did we really...

00:20:48.010 --> 00:20:48.930
Hmm?

00:20:49.230 --> 00:20:51.560
look that much like a real couple?

00:20:51.900 --> 00:20:53.370
Who knows?

00:20:53.370 --> 00:20:58.380
But personally, I could never imagine
a guy like me as your boyfriend.

00:20:58.380 --> 00:20:59.850
What do you mean "like you"?!

00:21:04.570 --> 00:21:08.830
I know you have a low opinion
of yourself, but that isn't right!

00:21:09.310 --> 00:21:12.200
I think you're a really
decent person, Amane-kun.

00:21:12.200 --> 00:21:16.300
You're kind, considerate, gentlemanly...

00:21:16.300 --> 00:21:19.530
and, um, I think you have a great personality.

00:21:20.120 --> 00:21:24.260
When you dress up, you look really good, too.

00:21:25.040 --> 00:21:26.900
R-Really?

00:21:27.530 --> 00:21:29.970
Um, thank you.

00:21:30.320 --> 00:21:33.240
So I mean, um, well...

00:21:33.240 --> 00:21:35.920
Don't be so hard on yourself!

00:21:35.920 --> 00:21:37.690
O-Okay...

00:21:39.780 --> 00:21:42.480
I'm... gonna wash the dishes!

00:21:42.480 --> 00:21:43.740
S-Sure!

00:21:55.260 --> 00:21:59.430
If you're gonna get that embarrassed,
why say it in the first place?

00:23:34.930 --> 00:23:39.930
Next Time
